## Summary (current)
- Phase 2 accomplished: directories created, property and performance tests moved, TestContainers tests migrated, `integration_test.rs` refactored, core E2E files split and helper functions consolidated in `tests/common/`.
- Remaining Phase 2 items (low effort): migrate remaining common module tests, add `mod.rs` roots and Cargo test entries, CI updates.

---

## Immediate Next Actions (Phase 3 - High Priority) ⚡
1. Split `e2e/api.rs` (293 tests) into per-feature files (upload/download/list/delete/search) — reduces test file size and improves parallelism. ✅ (planning)
2. Add contract tests (`tests/contract/`) for API schema/response contracts. ✅ (planned)
3. Configure `nextest` for faster, parallel test runs and better reporting.
4. Add snapshot testing for response shapes (`insta` or similar).
5. Finalize `mod.rs` roots and add `[[test]]` entries in `rust/Cargo.toml` to enable `cargo test --test <category>`. 

